    "updated_at": "2025-06-12T10:07:38Z",
    "body": "#1344 should contain rationale, IIRC the idea is to pick try to pick the executable-path as listed in `PATH` to avoid issues if a package manager like nix or scoop garbage-collects paths used by active shell sessions.\n\nIf you run starship with `PATH=`, you should get the expected executable.",
